WorkItem.Description:
Could we get the haste buff for the Madness of Deathwing added to the buffs tab?  It would be very nice to get my haste breakpoints right on my druid healer :).  Especially since my guild is doing that platform last.
 
I believe adding this to the end of GetDefaultBuffs() in Buff.cs should do the trick:
 
            defaultBuffs.Add(new Buff
            {
                Name = "Nozdormu's Presence",
                Source = "Nozdormu - Madness of Deathwing",
                Group = "Temporary Buffs",
                Stats = { SpellHaste = 0.2f, PhysicalHaste = 0.2f },
            });
